zWkylV9a1sIQ7kNvgFXN2zX&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AAxbal38dMAlD6gY3cjjR2z&oh=00_AYA6j_QtP2w9LXdRF5T8B1Ll29rEHgulddp7mbDwtykwhg&oe=66D5B4F8"}, {"file_name": "Pirte.png", "id": "1342580019826236", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984455_1342580023159569_1837107062568729337_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6nIBonBsVAsQ7kNvgE6_kpT&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AAxbal38dMAlD6gY3cjjR2z&oh=00_AYBSU0mE81Nbi2tDx_DyuMVdEQHRBJvQq-gI2EAlwuOqTA&oe=66D5AA88"}, {"file_name": "Bear.png", "id": "659574169386972", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75210897_659574172720305_6134549461054790666_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4vLVsHxr4DYQ7kNvgHAJUdZ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AAxbal38dMAlD6gY3cjjR2z&oh=00_AYD5RssaZhtUpBXTrPSUB1iO4RvI3Sv44yV4Rt_tAyomeg&oe=66D5B35A"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "16x9 Cover Image Meta 32 bit.png", "id": "504410531774601", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75221315_504410535107934_7382339972787947202_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=cft31MP_SaAQ7kNvgGeZZQw&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AAxbal38dMAlD6gY3cjjR2z&oh=00_AYD_b3ImdtnCWXQl90j2fq508sFbnsgCNI079BFGLUAJng&oe=66D59DD1"}, "display_name": "Colossal Cave ", "keywords": ["colossal", "cave", "williams", "adventure", "exploration"], "long_description": "\nFrom the acclaimed creator of King\u2019s Quest & Phantasmagoria, Colossal Cave, reimagined by Roberta Williams, is an exciting new action-adventure game that promises to bring you the adventure you\u2019ve longed for.\n\nAn homage to the esteemed classic text adventure, Colossal Cave Adventure by Will Crowther and Don Woods, Roberta Williams brings a beloved favorite game into the 21st century with meticulous handcrafted art, imaginative environmental creations based on actual caverns, rendering the vast and engaging cave in fully explorable three dimensional art.\n\nImmerse yourself in the mysterious and stunning world of boundless caverns and sweeping vistas, underground streams and hidden reservoirs - discover the many lost treasures, ancient civilizations, and encounter friends and foes alike in your quest to uncover the great mysteries of the mammoth cave system. With a non-linear exploration system, it\u2019s up to you to decide how to proceed through Colossal Cave, and how to discover all its secrets.\n\nThe ability to replay the game many times and still discover new things is what has kept this game in the hearts of generations of gamers for almost fifty years. If you think you know what adventure games are, you might be surprised to find out just how Colossal Cave defines the genre. Can you not only survive the Colossal Cave, but pass through it, and win all its secrets? Time will tell as you undertake the most exquisite and classic adventure ever - Colossal Cave!", "short_description": "Colossal Cave is an exciting new action-adventure game from the founders of Sierra On-Line, Ken and Roberta Williams. Immerse yourself in the world of Colossal Cave, explore its vast caverns and vistas, seek the diverse treasures within, and encounter both friends and foes in your quest to explore this mysterious and wonderful locale."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.colossalcave3d.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Cygnus Entertainment", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://colossalcave3d.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "ACTION", "EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "r